Description.Text: Please note the breakfast room area is under refurbishment, therefore the hotel will be providing box continental breakfast every morning, there will be no cooked breakfast until the refurbishment completed.
Situated in the South Kensington area, the hotel is just a couple of minutes walk from both Gloucester Road and Earls Court tube stations.
Both the bedrooms and bathrooms are small but very clean and in good condition. They are decorated simply, and are both modern and attractive.
It is a very modern, simple building with a 1990's feel.
The breakfast room has a very airy open feel,it is furnished with wooden furniture and bright decoration, creating a modern atmosphere. There is also a bar which is available throughout the day.
The modern lobby is also very bright with a small seating area and pale wooden floor; it is both bright and clean. The bar and restaurant are adjacent to this area.
